<plot>Sam Fisher is a wreck. He has lost the only thing that he has to live; his daughter, Sarah Burns, was hit and killed by a drunk driver. His superior, Irving Lambert, puts him undercover in the same prison cell with a man named Jamie Washington, who is a member of a terrorist organization called John Brown's Army. Fisher and Washington escape from the prison and Fisher is assigned to discover the JBA's plan, while remaining undercover.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?510865</url></doc>
